    <p class="text-gray-300">In Figure 5, the same experiment is performed. However, characteristic probability frequencies for all differentials of EDP(α, β) &gt; 2 &lt;sup&gt;−&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;sup&gt;33&lt;/sup&gt; that we observe during our search, are collected. A total of 53 differentials were found, and in Figure 5, we clearly see the same large differential effect for all 53 cases.</p>

