    <p class="text-gray-300">Note that the attack described so far uses an input difference of the form (α k 0). Thus, the impossible differentials described in this section can trivially be extended by two rounds on top of probability 1, as described in Section 3.4, yielding an extra 2 rounds attacked.</p>

